It's a simple SOAP interface which interacts with Amazon Mturk.
Install PHP 5.0.1 or higher, if not already installed.
Install PHP's SOAP extension, if not already installed. Odds are, if you're running PHP on Mac OS or Windows, the extension's already installed.
        CentOS/RedHat: yum install php-soap
        Debian/Ubuntu: apt-get install php5-soap 
Copy and paste applications folder atop your own codeigniter.

